title: Góra, Śrem County
text:
Góra () is a <a href="village">village</a> in the administrative district of <a href="Gmina%20%C5%9Arem">Gmina Śrem</a>, within <a href="%C5%9Arem%20County">Śrem County</a>, <a href="Greater%20Poland%20Voivodeship">Greater Poland Voivodeship</a>, in west-central Poland. It lies approximately north-west of <a href="%C5%9Arem">Śrem</a> and south of the regional capital <a href="Pozna%C5%84">Poznań</a>.
The village has a population of 200.
